    rdfs:comment 'Foreign key linking to plan.rate. Business justification: Billing premium rates are derived from plan-filed rates. This FK enables regulatory rate reconciliation, DOI audit trails, and premium accuracy validation — a health insurance billing analyst must tra' ;
